HEADWORD: Oquassa
<hw>O*quas"sa</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A
small, handsome trout (<spn>Salvelinus oquassa</spn>), found in some of
the lakes in Maine; -- called also <altname>blueback
trout</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
